This is a mixer plugin for the panel.

It supports the following audio systems:
	oss (default)
	alsa
	alsa (fallback via amixer)

Tuning the volume can be done by clicking in the indicator or by using the 
mouse wheel.

Installation: 
	tar zxvf xfce-mixer-<whatever>.tar.gz

	./configure # .........
	make
	make install

Cheers
	Danny
